"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.5.5\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.5.5</span> 標題：胸袋、胸牌（sacred pocket, breastpiece）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֹשֶׁן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： choshen)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:7\">EXO 25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4\">EXO 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:22\">EXO 28:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:23\">EXO 28:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:23\">EXO 28:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:24\">EXO 28:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:26\">EXO 28:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:28\">EXO 28:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:28\">EXO 28:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:29\">EXO 28:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:5\">EXO 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:9\">EXO 35:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:27\">EXO 35:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8\">EXO 39:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:9\">EXO 39:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:15\">EXO 39:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:16\">EXO 39:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:17\">EXO 39:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:19\">EXO 39:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:21\">EXO 39:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:21\">EXO 39:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:8\">LEV 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:8\">LEV 8:8</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0050_highpriest_breastpiece.png\" alt=\"OAI-0050_highpriest_breastpiece\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>胸袋是大祭司戴在胸前的一塊帶有刺繡的布，連接在以弗得的肩帶和腰帶之間（關於胸袋和以弗得的連接方式，參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.5.4 以弗得(ephod)&lt;REALIA:4.5.4&gt;</a> 中的描述）。</p>\n<p>胸袋呈長方形，長度是寬度的兩倍，對折後變成正方形。經文給出的尺寸是長2虎口，寬1虎口，對折後成為一個邊長1虎口的正方形。（通常認為，1虎口約等於半肘，參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:13\">EZK 43:13</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:17\">EZK 43:17</a> ，半肘約25厘米或10英吋）。折疊處在底部，這樣便形成一個口袋，裡面放著烏陵和土明（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.9.1 烏陵和土明(Urim and Thummim)&lt;REALIA:4.9.1&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<p>胸袋上的金槽裡鑲著四行寶石，每行三塊（或三行寶石，每行四塊）。十二塊寶石各不相同，每塊都刻著以色列一個支派的名字。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>要找到一個合適的術語來翻譯希伯來文<em>choshen</em> 可能並不容易。英文“breastplate”（以及中文「胸牌」）會讓人誤以為它是由金屬或其他堅硬的東西做成的。<em>Die Bibel: Einheitsübersetzung</em> （<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Bible in Basic English\">BE</abbr> ）作「籤袋」，著重於胸袋裡放著的烏陵和土明的功用。<em>Choshen</em> 也可譯作「聖袋」（“sacred pouch”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Moffatt Translation (1926)\">Mft</abbr> ）、「覆胸布」（“chest covering”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），或「心上的袋子」。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15\">EXO 28:15</a> 中的希伯來文短語<em>choshen mishpat</em> 被譯作“breastpiece of judgment”（「判斷的胸袋」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）、“pouch of judgment”（「判斷袋」；TOT ）、“judicial pouch”（「判決袋」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Moffatt Translation (1926)\">Mft</abbr> ）、“breastpiece of decision”（「決斷的胸袋」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> ），以及“breastpiece for making decisions”（「做決斷的胸袋」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 英文意為，「胸袋，大祭司用它來知道我要百姓去做什麼。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
